n. For modules in the blue and red positions you can choose different module styles. Take a look at the module variations page to get an overview.\r\n\r\n\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			\r\n			Module Positions\r\n		\r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			\r\n			Module Layouts\r\n		\r\n		\r\n			\r\n			Column Layouts\r\n		\r\n	\r\n', 'Events', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '45', '', '', '2012-02-25 08:50:38', '2012-02-25 08:50:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cloud/?p=45', 2, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
